- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is another possible category as the paper discusses the use of overlapping windows and speculation to improve the efficiency of complex event processing.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper proposes a new approach to parallel processing of complex event streams.
